===卡米拉·瓦莉娃争议事件===
{{See also|2022年冬季奥林匹克运动会花样滑冰比赛}}
原定于2月8日进行的[[2022年冬季奥林匹克运动会花样滑冰团体比赛|花样滑冰团体比赛的颁奖仪式]]未能按计划进行，对此[[国际奥林匹克委员会|国际奥林匹克委员会]]发言人马克·亚当斯（{{lang|en|Mark Adams}}）解释称，推迟颁奖典礼是因为需要与[[国际滑冰联盟|国际滑冰联盟]]进行“法律咨询”<ref>{{Cite web|date=2022-02-09|title=Olympic medals in team figure skating delayed by legal issue|url=https://apnews.com/article/winter-olympics-figure-skating-sports-international-olympic-committee-court-of-arbitration-for-sport-c49077705737be8a7d41a2847c2f355b|access-date=2022-02-09|website=[[美联社|The Associated Press]]|archive-date=2022-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220209061349/https://apnews.com/article/winter-olympics-figure-skating-sports-international-olympic-committee-court-of-arbitration-for-sport-c49077705737be8a7d41a2847c2f355b}}</ref>。2月11日，瑞典斯德哥尔摩反兴奋剂实验室發表了一份去年12月對俄奧委運動員卡米拉·瓦利耶娃實施的藥檢報告，稱其藥檢樣本疑似對禁药[[曲美他嗪|曲美他嗪]]呈阳性反應<ref>{{Cite news|last1=Tétrault-Farber|first1=Gabrielle|last2=Axon|first2=Iain|last3=Grohmann|first3=Karolos|date=2022-02-09|title=Figure skating-Russian media say teen star tested positive for banned drug|publisher=[[路透社|Reuters]]|url=https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/sports/figure-skating-medals-ceremony-delayed-over-legal-consultation-2022-02-09/|access-date=2022-02-09|archive-date=2022-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220209062431/https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/sports/figure-skating-medals-ceremony-delayed-over-legal-consultation-2022-02-09/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/olympics/beijing/2022/02/09/olympic-figure-skating-team-medals-delayed-russian-drug-test/6717526001/|title=Positive drug test by Russian Kamila Valieva has forced a delay of Olympic team medals ceremony|first=Christine|last=Brennan|publisher=[[今日美国|USA Today]]|date=2022-02-09|access-date=2022-02-19|archive-date=2022-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220209113551/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/olympics/beijing/2022/02/09/olympic-figure-skating-team-medals-delayed-russian-drug-test/6717526001/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这是在2021年12月25日俄罗斯花样滑冰锦标赛期间取得的血样，直到2月8日该样品还没有被[[世界反兴奋剂机构|世界反兴奋剂机构]]（WADA）实验室分析检测。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2022/02/10/sports/olympics/kamila-valieva-trimetazidine.html|title=Star Russian Figure Skater Tested Positive for Banned Drug|first1=Juliet|last1=Macur|first2=Andrew|last2=Keh|publisher=[[紐約時報|The New York Times]]|date=2022-02-12|access-date=2022-02-17|archive-date=2022-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220211035034/https://www.nytimes.com/2022/02/10/sports/olympics/kamila-valieva-trimetazidine.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

俄罗斯反兴奋剂机构（RUSADA）最初决定对瓦利耶娃实施临时禁赛，在运动员提出上诉后，于2月9日取消了禁赛。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1119148/rusada-beijing-2022-valieva-sample|title=RUSADA blames COVID-19 wave for delayed analysis of Valieva sample|first=Michael|last=Pavitt|work=Inside the Games|date=2022-02-12|access-date=2022-02-17|archive-date=2022-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220212045934/https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1119148/rusada-beijing-2022-valieva-sample|dead-url=no}}</ref>就在她被临时禁赛的一天后，国际奥委会、世界反兴奋剂机构和国际滑冰联盟向国际体育仲裁法庭提出抗议。2月12日，RUSADA和国际奥委会宣布他们将拓宽各自的调查的范围，包括她的随从成员（如教练、团队医生等等）。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.skysports.com/more-sports/winter-olympics/news/30787/12539761/kamila-valieva-ioc-welcomes-investigation-of-russian-figure-skaters-entourage-as-15-year-old-awaits-cas-decision-at-winter-olympics|title=Kamila Valieva: IOC welcomes investigation of Russian figure skater's entourage as 15-year-old awaits CAS decision at Winter Olympics|author=PA Media|publisher=Sky Sports|date=2022-02-12|access-date=2022-02-17|archive-date=2022-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220212082818/https://www.skysports.com/more-sports/winter-olympics/news/30787/12539761/kamila-valieva-ioc-welcomes-investigation-of-russian-figure-skaters-entourage-as-15-year-old-awaits-cas-decision-at-winter-olympics|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2月13日晚上，国际体育仲裁法庭召集IOC、WADA、ISU、RUSADA、ROC代表和瓦利耶娃本人在北京的临时办公室召开视频听证会。一天后，国际体育仲裁法庭宣布驳回上诉，允许瓦利耶娃参加女子单人滑比赛。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://thehill.com/policy/international/russia/593979-russian-figure-skaters-drug-case-to-be-heard-sunday-in-beijing|title=Russian figure skater's drug test case to be heard Sunday|first=Lexi|last=Lonas|website=The Hill|date=2022-02-12|access-date=2022-02-17|archive-date=2022-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220212152356/https://thehill.com/policy/international/russia/593979-russian-figure-skaters-drug-case-to-be-heard-sunday-in-beijing|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://amp.cnn.com/cnn/2022/02/10/sport/kamila-valieva-roc-drugs-test-olympics-spt-intl-hnk/index.html|title=Kamila Valieva: Russian anti-doping agency allowed teenage figure skater to compete in Olympics despite failed drug test|last1=Ritchie|first1=Hannah|last2=Watson|first2=Angus|last3=Regan|first3=Helen|date=2022-02-11|website=[[有线电视新闻网|CNN]]|access-date=2022-02-12|archive-date=2022-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220211042440/https://amp.cnn.com/cnn/2022/02/10/sport/kamila-valieva-roc-drugs-test-olympics-spt-intl-hnk/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>国际体育仲裁法庭裁定，由于瓦利耶娃作为未成年人，在WADA的规则下被归类为“受保护的人”，同时她在冬奥期间的药检样本未检测出阳性反应，另外，检测结果通知不及时，“损害了运动员为自己的利益建立某些法律要求的能力”，“并非运动员的过错”<ref>{{cite web|date=2022-02-14|title=Russian skater Kamila Valieva cleared to compete at Olympics|url=https://apnews.com/article/winter-olympics-kamila-valieva-doping-decision-0dd063b5092681697525b69cd0c7212d|access-date=2022-02-14|publisher=Associated Press|archive-date=2022-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220214060911/https://apnews.com/article/winter-olympics-kamila-valieva-doping-decision-0dd063b5092681697525b69cd0c7212d|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite press release|url=https://www.tas-cas.org/fileadmin/user_upload/CAS_Ad_Hoc_Media_Release_Beijing_8.pdf|title=The CAS Ad Hoc Division Declines to Impose a Provisional Suspension on the Russian Figure Skater Kamila Valieva|publisher=[[国际体育仲裁法庭|Court of Arbitration for Sport]]|date=2022-02-14|access-date=2022-02-17|archive-date=2022-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220214151257/https://www.tas-cas.org/fileadmin/user_upload/CAS_Ad_Hoc_Media_Release_Beijing_8.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在国际体育仲裁法庭公布判决结果后，国际奥委会宣布，在瓦利耶娃的兴奋剂阳性事件调查结果公布前，不会为团体比赛前三名的队伍颁发奖牌，如果瓦利耶娃在女子单人滑项目上进入前三名，也同样不会在调查结束前为该项目前三名颁发奖牌。另外，国际奥委会还要求国际滑冰联盟在瓦利耶娃进入女子单人滑短节目前24名的情况下，允许获得第25名的选手参加自由滑阶段。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://olympics.com/ioc/news/ioc-eb-decides-no-medal-ceremonies-following-cas-decision-on-the-case-of-roc-skater|title=IOC EB decides no medal ceremonies following CAS decision on the case of ROC skater|work=IOC|date=2022-02-14|access-date=2022-02-17|archive-date=2022-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220214101407/https://olympics.com/ioc/news/ioc-eb-decides-no-medal-ceremonies-following-cas-decision-on-the-case-of-roc-skater|dead-url=no}}</ref>瓦利耶娃最终在女子单人滑自由滑阶段发挥失常，数次摔倒，获得第四名，颁奖仪式也因此正常举行<ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/olympics/2022/02/17/figure-skating-medals-ceremony/ |title= In an Olympic upset, winning figure skaters get a medal ceremony after all |first= Chuck |last= Culpepper |publisher= [[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] |date= 2022-02-17 |accessdate=2022-05-11 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/VzB3D |archivedate=2022-05-11 }}</ref>。

[[美国奥林匹克与残疾人奥林匹克委员会|美国奥林匹克与残疾人奥林匹克委员会]]对于国际奥委会无限期推迟团体比赛颁奖典礼的决定表示不满，称这对运动员并不公平<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.firstpost.com/sports/beijing-winter-olympics-2022-us-olympic-ceo-says-decision-to-not-award-figure-skating-medals-unfair-to-athletes-10383681.html|title=Beijing Winter Olympics 2022: US Olympic CEO says decision to not award figure skating medals 'unfair to athletes'|publisher=Firstpost|date=2022-02-17|accessdate=2022-05-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220217122003/https://www.firstpost.com/sports/beijing-winter-olympics-2022-us-olympic-ceo-says-decision-to-not-award-figure-skating-medals-unfair-to-athletes-10383681.html|archivedate=2022-02-17}}</ref>。美国队曾一度向国际体育仲裁法庭提出申诉，要求为代表该国参加团体比赛的九名队员颁发银牌，然而申诉最终遭到驳回<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/team-usa-figure-skating-beijing-olympics-11645270899|title=Arbitration Panel Rejects Bid from U.S. Figure Skaters to Receive Silver Medals in Beijing|publisher=The Wall Street Journal|date=2022-02-19|accessdate=2022-05-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220220234732/https://www.wsj.com/articles/team-usa-figure-skating-beijing-olympics-11645270899|archivedate=2022-02-20}}</ref>。国际奥委会考虑为分别位列团体赛第二和第三名的美国队和日本队赠送奥运火炬以临时代替奖牌<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1119396/figure-skating-torches-valieva-beijing22|title=Figure skaters to get Olympic Torches instead of medals for team event as Valieva case continues|work=Inside the Games|date=2022-02-17|accessdate=2022-05-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220217075102/https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1119396/figure-skating-torches-valieva-beijing22|archivedate=2022-02-17}}</ref>。

2月15日，国际奥委会资深成员丹尼斯·奥斯瓦尔德（{{lang|en|Denis Oswald}}）透露，据瓦利耶娃自己解释称，药检阳性可能受到了祖父服用的某种药物的影响。他的祖父在服用了治疗心脏病的药物之后，杯子里的饮用水里残留了一些药物，瓦利耶娃不慎使用了被药物污染的水杯。<ref>{{Cite web|title=外媒：瓦利耶娃药检阳性原因曝光 或与其祖父的心脏病药物有关|url=https://news.sina.com.cn/o/2022-02-15/doc-ikyamrna0920009.shtml|access-date=2022-02-17|date=2022-02-15|last=中国新闻网|work=新浪体育|archive-date=2022-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220215125516/https://news.sina.com.cn/o/2022-02-15/doc-ikyamrna0920009.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>《纽约时报》的一篇报道表示瓦利耶娃的祖父录制了一段视频给听证会，证实自己确实服用了曲美他嗪。<ref>{{Cite web|title=媒体：瓦利耶娃祖父证实服用曲美他嗪|url=https://sputniknews.cn/20220217/1039333583.html|date=2022-02-17|access-date=2022-02-17|publisher=俄罗斯卫星通讯社|archive-date=2022-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220217171141/https://sputniknews.cn/20220217/1039333583.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>3月中旬，世界反兴奋剂机构要求俄罗斯反兴奋剂机构在8月8日前提交和瓦利耶娃相关的报告<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rt.com/sport/552286-figure-skating-valieva-wada-deadline/|title=WADA announces Valieva deadline decision|publisher=RT|date=2022-03-19|accessdate=2022-06-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220319184708/https://www.rt.com/sport/552286-figure-skating-valieva-wada-deadline/|archivedate=2022-03-19}}</ref>。

